Package source.exception

package source.exception
  • Exceptions
    Class
    Description
    CampFullException
    Represents the exception for when the camp is full by generating a message for the user.
    CampNotFoundException
    Represents exception for when camp is not found
    CommitteeWithdrawException
    Represents exception for when camp committee tries to withdraw from camp
    DateAfterDateException
    Represents an exception to ensure that the end date set exceeds the start date
    DateClashException
    Represents an exception for when there is a clash in date between any 2 camps.
    DeadlineOverException
    Represents the exception for when a camp registration deadline has passed
    ExceedMaximumException
    Represents an exception for when the maximum capacity of a camp has been exceeded.
    InvalidUserGroupException
    Represents an exception for when the camp is not yet opened to the student user yet.
    MultipleCommitteeRoleException
    Represents an exception that limits camp committee members to only be the camp committee member for one camp.
    NoAccessException
    Represents an exception for when the user does not have access
    UserNotFoundException
    Represents an exception for when user is not found in the camps registration
    WithdrawnException
    Represents an exception for when the student has already withdrawn from the camp before
